### Sabit Daily Actions API Test
### Use this file with REST Client extension in VSCode

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "muslim@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "displayName": "Abdullah"
}

### 2. Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "muslim@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Extract token (automatic with REST Client)
@token = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### 3. Record Fajr Prayer
POST {{baseUrl}}/daily/actions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "actionType": "PRAYER",
  "metadata": {
    "prayerName": "Fajr",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-07T05:30:00Z"
  }
}

### 4. Record Tasbeeh (100 times)
POST {{baseUrl}}/daily/actions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "actionType": "TASBEEH",
  "metadata": {
    "count": 100,
    "type": "SubhanAllah"
  }
}

### 5. Record Charity
POST {{baseUrl}}/daily/actions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "actionType": "CHARITY",
  "metadata": {
    "amount": 10,
    "currency": "USD",
    "cause": "Orphan support"
  }
}

### 6. Record Morning Azkar
POST {{baseUrl}}/daily/actions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "actionType": "AZKAR",
  "metadata": {
    "type": "morning",
    "completed": true
  }
}

### 7. Get Today's Actions
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily/actions/today
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get Last 7 Days Actions
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily/actions?days=7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Get Last 30 Days Actions
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily/actions?days=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Check Prayer Streak
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily/streak?actionType=PRAYER
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Check Tasbeeh Streak
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily/streak?actionType=TASBEEH
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Check Charity Streak
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily/streak?actionType=CHARITY
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Check Azkar Streak
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily/streak?actionType=AZKAR
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 14. Get User Profile (check XP and coins earned)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 15. Get Quote of the Day (Public - no auth needed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily/quote

